<span class="displaytext">the (candidate last) campaign today announced the endorsement of the transportation communications union. tcu has 65,000 active and retired members, mostly employed in the railroad industry. <p>"the best candidate for our members and all of labor is (candidate full)," said tcu president bob scardelletti. "she gives american workers the best opportunity to have a friend in the white house and a strong advocate for their issues. " </p><p>tcu is an affiliate of the international association of machinists and aerospace workers, which has also endorsed hillary. </p><p>"i am honored to receive the support of the transportation communications union," (candidate last) said. "america's working families will not be invisible to my administration." </p><p>the iam and its more than 700,000 members and the united transportation union and its 125,000 members endorsed (candidate last) last week.</p></span>



